            "body": "Seems to only happen when window size is unchanged.\n\nThis change can fix this specific problem:\n```diff\ndiff --git a/src/nvim/terminal.c b/src/nvim/terminal.c\nindex 08eb4f2066..75d7cd5d21 100644\n--- a/src/nvim/terminal.c\n+++ b/src/nvim/terminal.c\n@@ -677,7 +677,7 @@ void terminal_check_size(Terminal *term)\n   vterm_set_size(term->vt, height, width);\n   vterm_screen_flush_damage(term->vts);\n   term->pending.resize = true;\n-  invalidate_terminal(term, -1, -1);\n+  refresh_terminal(term);\n }\n \n static void set_terminal_winopts(TerminalState *const s)\n```\nbut will cause other problems.",
